Chimera printing service is a jon-rpc server that processes jasperreports reports and fills them with the information received through calls to the service.

It consists of 3 parts:
-server. Json-rpc server processing calls
-customer. PyQt6 interface in charge of viewing the status of the server and managing printers and models.
-daemon. Allows you to install and / or remove the chimeraps service on the host operating system.

Instalación:
Requerimientos:
* Java JRE 9 (probado con OpenJDK 11 en windows) (Setear JAVA_HOME)
* Ghostscript (probado con 9.55 en windows)


Windows.
En consola con provilegios de administrador ejecutamos:
pip install quimeraps

Linux
sudo -H pip3 install quimeraps



Instalación servício:
quimeraps_daemon install

Desinstalacion servício:
quimera_daemon remove

Para comprobar si el servico/demónio funciona correctamente.
quimeraps_sever








